you think it's interesting

88
00:06:03,162 --> 00:06:04,959
the extent to which
we seem to still have

89
00:06:05,064 --> 00:06:08,397
the image of the sword,
the concept of the sword,

90
00:06:08,501 --> 00:06:10,662
the symbolic importance
of the sword.

91
00:06:10,770 --> 00:06:13,238
I mean, it's hard to
turn on the television

92
00:06:13,339 --> 00:06:15,273
