of a well-loved and deceased

915
00:53:34,678 --> 00:53:38,774
archaeologist was literally
saved from history's dust bin.

916
00:53:38,882 --> 00:53:46,379
The treasure inside:
a sword, 13 centuries old.

917
00:53:46,489 --> 00:53:49,390
Since then the sword has been
tested extensively

918
00:53:49,492 --> 00:53:52,325
by the Royal Armories and
the Bamburgh Research Project

919
00:53:52,429 --> 00:53:54,294
in a effort to
unlock the secrets

920
00:53:54,397 --> 00:53:57,560
of this rare object's
hidden past.

921
00:53:57,667 --> 00:54:00,693
This is one of the most
significant swords found

922
00:54:00,804 --> 00:54:03,932
