00:54:12,749 --> 00:54:16,742
When you hold it today it has an
almost mystical quality to it.

926
00:54:16,853 --> 00:54:20,380
It looks like a corroded lump
of metal but in its glory

927
00:54:20,490 --> 00:54:24,290
this would have been
an awe inspiring sight.

928
00:54:24,394 --> 00:54:26,385
The x-rays revealed
it to be an extraordinarily

929
00:54:26,496 --> 00:54:29,397
sophisticated piece
of technology.

930
00:54:29,499 --> 00:54:32,900
It proved to be
an incredibly important weapon.

931
00:54:33,003 --> 00:54:34,800
One of the most
important weapons,

932
00:54:34,904 --> 00:54:38,772
I think it's fair to say,
ever found in Britain.

933
00:54:38,875 --> 00:54:42,606
