949
00:55:21,718 --> 00:55:24,915
If a warrior would go
into battle with a sword

950
00:55:25,021 --> 00:55:27,888
that was excessively
hard and brittle

951
00:55:27,991 --> 00:55:31,427
the battle for him could be
very short indeed.

952
00:55:31,528 --> 00:55:34,497
There's only a handful
like this in the world,

953
00:55:34,597 --> 00:55:37,191
probably four or five
in the entire world.

954
00:55:37,300 --> 00:55:38,597
Experts we've talked to in

955
00:55:38,702 --> 00:55:42,035
the British Museum
of the Royal Armories

956
00:55:42,138 --> 00:55:45,107
don't know of a single example
of a six stranded sword

957
00:55:45,208 --> 00:55:48,143
prior to this one being
identified which does suggest

958
00:55:48,244 --> 00:55:50,075
that they are-
something of this

959
00:55:50,180 --> 00:55:53,411
technological sophistication
is staggeringly rare.

960
00:55:53,516 --> 00:55:56,644
If you were actually have looked
